1299.name: L-Ag40Sn
1299.Applications: Brazing a weight range of different metals in maintanance and repair with excelent strenght, Boiler making, tubing, cooling equipment etc. Do not use this alloy above working temperatures of 200ºC .
1299.Suitable_For: Brazing: Steels, Copper, Copper alloys, Stainless steel, Nickel and Nickel alloys. Also suitable for dissimilar joints between these metals.
